Cyberpunk style: A towering, chaotic machine made of hundreds of interconnected glowing server racks, cables, and circuit boards forming a menacing labyrinth in a dark neon-lit industrial space. The structure spirals upward like a digital tower of Babel, with sparks flying between components and holographic data streams tangling into knots. In stark contrast, a single sleek monolith stands nearby, elegant and simple, emitting a calm blue glow—pristine and uncluttered. Steam rises from grated floors, magenta and cyan lights reflect off wet metal surfaces, and the atmosphere conveys the overwhelming weight of unnecessary complexity versus elegant simplicity.
